{"tid":1632201,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"運動處於被動 短期運動方向","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:26:33.000Z","uid":164325,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f2dc5fa0b70e96f0abcad7b760ad189cdbe29d38","tid":1632201,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"林鄭推行緊急法，推《禁蒙面法》下稱《蒙》，如運動激烈化，結果就是暴徒暴力升級，更加需要《蒙》。如運動日漸平靜，結果就是《蒙》行之有效。<br />\n<br />\n以下會提出幾方面既重點予各位討論。在各連登post與TG群分別有不同看法。而本人將整理及加入自己看法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 美國民主人權法</span></strong></span><br />\n美國要介入香港事務，最有力既借口就是中英聯合聲明及基本法給港人的自由。因此，運動方向必須緊貼五大訴求-<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真普選</span></span></strong>。<br />\n另外，要配合美國落實法案。中共港共一直強調此法案是美國粗暴干涉中港內政，但實際上，此案只是美國內部的一條法案而已。要讓社會知道，粗暴干涉別國內政的是中港共。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 中槍事件</span></strong></span><br />\n黑警武力進化到真槍實彈，仿佛視人命如無物。前線黑警情緒失控，如精神病人手執致命武器。對公眾安全是極大危險。<span style=\"color: green;\">政府和警隊企業利用《蒙》掩蓋開真槍嚴重性，企圖讓大眾&ldquo;習慣&rdquo;</span>。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須煲大這核彈。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 禁蒙面法/緊急法</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>文宣戰重大戰場。</strong></span></span>必須強調及誇大禁蒙面法/緊急法後果。例如《蒙》=人臉識別&gt;監控&gt;入獄。《緊》=資產充公，一無所有。另外，美國戰線要強調侵犯自由同個人私隱。國際線要強調阻礙記者採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">4. 裝備/鶳</span></strong></span><br />\n請參考黃藍紅黑。<br />\n鶳必須出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">5. Marketing</span></strong></span><br />\n做生意要marketing，抗爭都一樣。<span style=\"color: green;\">針對國際對香港運動慢慢失去興趣，是否要想想新招數?</span><br />\n例如 : <br />\n同爆眼少女一樣，中彈少年 &gt; 放一片柒紅紗布遊行。<br />\n一國兩制已死遊行<br />\n黑西裝遊行 etc<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>6. 整理黑警暴行</strong></span></span><br />\n連登已有人整理，請繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">7. 前線繼續以對抗黑警，保持不畏強權，勇敢對抗的形象。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9d7920f9b37a18bbef470da2a6cfba7b409acd9d","tid":1632201,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！ 而家只係要你入黎推post</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"62a6ed543433ff00288f35e8ef7fb937e671a10d","tid":1632201,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"64f780e06de44d7bd95bc00d4adb40087d32a6a0","tid":1632201,"uid":85681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"532a3532cd27d2ad392a8589cb29c8201b3dade9","tid":1632201,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"自推x1"},{"pid":"ff734e0d9cb5a20698e6cec1684f1531c6f625ce","tid":1632201,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"緊急法就正正係焦土，大家文宣要將兩樣野連結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b173fc215b312c78ebc145e5e68d9c798a6d03b6","tid":1632201,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"b155c45f70edeb20043049e1d2a1347e96c0db7b","tid":1632201,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:04.000Z","msg":"黑西裝遊行正"},{"pid":"704b2882decfefb0efb50c261639c9d7ffc67349","tid":1632201,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"7e9a2074c348c163995e28ced615418a879eed8e","tid":1632201,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家太過focus係蒙面法 裝修 私了 忽略左緊急法帶來既經濟危機 大家要明白呢一點 呢個係港共最大春袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1dccf66eb59753f9928e825eafd83617214cf30","tid":1632201,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:31.000Z","msg":"呢類行動Post永遠冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[行動Post] 請大家今晚開始穩固返好文宣戰線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejkCGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejkCGS</a>"},{"pid":"986706fb8a0aaaf1f2006ad1d716307e9b20ecb8","tid":1632201,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1dccf66eb59753f9928e825eafd83617214cf30","tid":1632201,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:31.000Z","msg":"呢類行動Post永遠冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[行動Post] 請大家今晚開始穩固返好文宣戰線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejkCGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejkCGS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5300592fba5eeb68797ce56845ceb4c762c2a2","tid":1632201,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2dc5fa0b70e96f0abcad7b760ad189cdbe29d38","tid":1632201,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"林鄭推行緊急法，推《禁蒙面法》下稱《蒙》，如運動激烈化，結果就是暴徒暴力升級，更加需要《蒙》。如運動日漸平靜，結果就是《蒙》行之有效。<br />\n<br />\n以下會提出幾方面既重點予各位討論。在各連登post與TG群分別有不同看法。而本人將整理及加入自己看法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 美國民主人權法</span></strong></span><br />\n美國要介入香港事務，最有力既借口就是中英聯合聲明及基本法給港人的自由。因此，運動方向必須緊貼五大訴求-<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真普選</span></span></strong>。<br />\n另外，要配合美國落實法案。中共港共一直強調此法案是美國粗暴干涉中港內政，但實際上，此案只是美國內部的一條法案而已。要讓社會知道，粗暴干涉別國內政的是中港共。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 中槍事件</span></strong></span><br />\n黑警武力進化到真槍實彈，仿佛視人命如無物。前線黑警情緒失控，如精神病人手執致命武器。對公眾安全是極大危險。<span style=\"color: green;\">政府和警隊企業利用《蒙》掩蓋開真槍嚴重性，企圖讓大眾&ldquo;習慣&rdquo;</span>。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須煲大這核彈。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 禁蒙面法/緊急法</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>文宣戰重大戰場。</strong></span></span>必須強調及誇大禁蒙面法/緊急法後果。例如《蒙》=人臉識別&gt;監控&gt;入獄。《緊》=資產充公，一無所有。另外，美國戰線要強調侵犯自由同個人私隱。國際線要強調阻礙記者採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">4. 裝備/鶳</span></strong></span><br />\n請參考黃藍紅黑。<br />\n鶳必須出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">5. Marketing</span></strong></span><br />\n做生意要marketing，抗爭都一樣。<span style=\"color: green;\">針對國際對香港運動慢慢失去興趣，是否要想想新招數?</span><br />\n例如 : <br />\n同爆眼少女一樣，中彈少年 &gt; 放一片柒紅紗布遊行。<br />\n一國兩制已死遊行<br />\n黑西裝遊行 etc<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>6. 整理黑警暴行</strong></span></span><br />\n連登已有人整理，請繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">7. 前線繼續以對抗黑警，保持不畏強權，勇敢對抗的形象。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">8. 區議會</span></strong></span><br />\n文宣力撐泛民<br />\n連結抗爭運動<br />\n政黑藍警暴行<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重擊建制派</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9d1ab98465ac8b9d66cc18deba5a63967be56d2e","tid":1632201,"uid":132208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:10.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線 x USA <br />\nRecall 5 demands focus<br />\n<br />\nstabilise 人權法基礎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主動出擊<br />\n樣樣都要做"},{"pid":"a219321a949ade9466840df5a37da2144e1adfff","tid":1632201,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:00.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"964de2ac098b2dd2182321c51591638fbd3ca36f","tid":1632201,"uid":296375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得不如全世界集中推全民口罩活動 無限期日常生活帶口罩 將抗爭融入日常生活 比和理非有得再重新慢慢參與番 凝聚民心 比全世界知香港人對抗惡法既心<br />\n<br />\n目標係要做到唔帶口罩係少數!!!!!"},{"pid":"b296771e64e55c3a53a35960ade9d456988f7712","tid":1632201,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"陳同佳出獄大日子應該有咩活動好？"},{"pid":"12f660ab54a6bc0641d4f59a286a8ef2e672f7d6","tid":1632201,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"支持！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一個準則可以破到而家死局</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b95f994522665222d2a4946df3e907d98f797d3d","tid":1632201,"uid":36034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0f20ec056f0a336db4993fa77fd51c0c2e0e1e0e","tid":1632201,"uid":106945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:09:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36aaf5079b4c734508a70d8663ff36cc8f799a1b","tid":1632201,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:37:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1d81c57169d845665f4c6cf2969df6ebfd3d49c","tid":1632201,"uid":164325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c3f664